            "id": 6404227,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 集中市場加權指數上漲1413.54點至33136.53點，漲幅4.46%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間01日01:06，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1413.54點（或4.46%），暫報33136.53點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-2.73%</li><li>近 1 月：-10.42%</li><li>近 3 月：+9.53%</li><li>近 6 月：+22.86%</li><li>今年以來：+9.53%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>Flash模組概念領漲+6.78%。其中    宇瞻(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8271:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8271\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8271-TW</a>)            上漲        10%            ;        宜鼎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5289:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5289\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5289-TW</a>)            上漲        9.92%            ;        立萬利(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3054:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3054\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3054-TW</a>)            上漲        9.91%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>DRAM模組概念領漲+5.90%。其中    宇瞻(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8271:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8271\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8271-TW</a>)            上漲        10%            ;        宜鼎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5289:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5289\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5289-TW</a>)            上漲        9.92%            ;        立萬利(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3054:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3054\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3054-TW</a>)            上漲        9.91%    。</p></section></main>",
